  <brief_title>Brain-derived Neurotrophic Factor Participates in Visceral Hyperalgesia in Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Brain-derived Neurotrophic Factor in Visceral Hyperalgesia in IBS Patients</official_title>
